schools.name: Youree Dr. Middle Advanced Placement Magnet School

data.description:
This charming white brick home offers a cozy and inviting atmosphere. Featuring a modern, updated kitchen, complete with a convenient walk-in laundry and pantry, it's perfect for today's busy lifestyle. The main bathroom has been thoughtfully updated, offering a tub and shower combo for your comfort.

The main bedroom is spacious and provides ample storage for your belongings. Additionally, the property offers two covered parking spots, ensuring your vehicles are protected from the elements. Large backyard, perfect for entertaining. Alarm equipment to remain as well as washer and dryer.
